  "texts": [
    "As for the DWT implementation, it iteratively passes through low-pass and high-pass filters.",
    "Given the focus on temporal channels, which are four in total, the computation of features is split such that four cores are allocated to computing the FFT, while another set of four cores are allocated to the DWT.",
    "This results in two cores per channel dedicated to feature extraction.",
    "The optimized artifact detection models generated by TPOT are mainly Extra Trees, i.e., an ensemble of Decision Trees (DTs) 60.",
    "The obtained DTs can hardly fit on an embedded platform (they feature millions of threshold values)."
  ],
